        <p className="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-slate-400 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-sans font-extralight">
          Pare de adivinhar. Nossa IA analisa 50+ pontos do seu rosto para recomendar o estilo exato que maximiza sua estética.
        </p>

        <div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 w-full justify-center">
          <button 
            onClick={onStartVisagism}
            className="group relative flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-lime-400 hover:bg-lime-300 text-slate-900 font-normal font-economica text-3xl py-5 px-12 rounded-full transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(163,230,53,0.3)] tracking-wide uppercase"
          >
            <Sparkles className="w-6 h-6 fill-slate-900 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform" />
            Análise de Visagismo
          </button>

          <button 
            onClick={onStartScheduling}
            className="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-[#1c1c1e] hover:bg-[#2c2c2e] text-white font-normal font-economica text-3xl py-5 px-12 rounded-full border border-white/5 transition-all hover:border-white/20 tracking-wide uppercase"
          >
            <Calendar className="w-6 h-6" />
            Agendar Agora
          </button>
