               </div>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-[#1c1c1e] rounded-[32px] p-8 border border-white/5 flex flex-col flex-grow">
              <h3 className="text-3xl font-medium font-sans uppercase tracking-wider text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span className="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#2c2c2e] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">3</span>
                Horários Disponíveis
